const REDIRECT_URI = process.env.REACT_APP_REDIRECT_URL;

export const KAKAO_AUTH_URL = `https://kauth.kakao.com/oauth/authorize?client_id=9878f146abba1b592f7e00cd697887b4&redirect_uri=${REDIRECT_URI}&response_type=code`;
